iconservicesd(1) General Commands Manual iconservicesd(1)

NAME

iconservicesd — deamon responsible for managing the shared icon cache.

SYNOPSIS

iconservicesd

DESCRIPTION

iconservicesd is used by the system to add and remove images to/from shared icon cache.

FILES

/System/Library/CoreServices/iconservicesd
executable

SEE ALSO

iconservicesagent iconutil
